Problem Statement

Create a Spring application for a Library Management System.

A library allows users to borrow books, and the borrowing process depends on a Notification Service to inform the user.

Requirements

Create an interface NotificationService.

Create an implementation class EmailNotificationService.

Create a class LibraryService.

LibraryService should depend on NotificationService.

Use Spring Dependency Injection to inject the dependency.

When a book is borrowed, a notification should be sent to the user.

Expected Output
Book borrowed successfully
Notification sent via Email 
